N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 129.4 - Education and training

State Regulations

Victim assistance education and training
shall be given to judicial and nonjudicial personnel of the Unified Court

System so that victims may be promptly, properly and completely
assisted. Notes
